            "title": "天氣「濕完再凍」！天文台料周四五濕度高達100%  冷鋒殺到下周一多區低見13°C",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"天氣「濕完再凍」！天文台料周四五濕度高達100%  冷鋒殺到下周一多區低見13°C\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/919a4366a1a3cda65cc7f5b8c526ac62/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031011590438972.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">天氣「濕完再凍」！天文台料周四五濕度高達100%  冷鋒殺到下周一多區低見13°C</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【天氣/天文台/濕凍/潮濕/冷鋒】香港濕凍世一？天文台今日（10日）表示，現時影響廣東沿岸的偏東氣流會在未來兩三日逐漸緩和並被一股海洋氣流取代，該區日間溫暖，本周中後期潮濕有霧。天文台預料一道冷鋒會在周六（15日）橫過華南並為該區帶來驟雨，受隨後的乾燥東北季候風影響，下周初華南沿岸天氣轉涼，天色好轉。\n\n</p><h2>冷鋒周六橫過華南 周日氣溫急降</h2>\n<p>據天文台九天天氣預測，周四（13日）大致多雲，日間部分時間有陽光及溫暖。早晚有一兩陣微雨，沿岸有霧，周四及周五（13至14日）相對濕度均高達100%。不過，隨着一道冷鋒會在周六（15日）橫過華南，周日（16日）起氣溫急降，一夜跌9度至最低15度，周一（17日）新界多區氣溫更低見13度。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"現時影響廣東沿岸的偏東氣流會在未來兩三日逐漸緩和並被一股海洋氣流取代。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a0b613aa8e901c47869532d956c73655/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250302_191930560.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現時影響廣東沿岸的偏東氣流會在未來兩三日逐漸緩和並被一股海洋氣流取代。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預測。天文台網站截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/77e070744536965098eb1cee6f35c19c/2025-03/2025-03-10_115551.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預測。天文台網站截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"該區日間溫暖，本周中後期潮濕有霧。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd25bcc739b0a0b9860f464db301fb65/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250226_172540098_16.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        該區日間溫暖，本周中後期潮濕有霧。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"天文台預料一道冷鋒會在周六（15日）橫過華南並為該區帶來驟雨。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ecc295c0103c5172787a92dd74e9be22/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250226_172540098_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        天文台預料一道冷鋒會在周六（15日）橫過華南並為該區帶來驟雨。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"受隨後的乾燥東北季候風影響，下周初華南沿岸天氣轉涼，天色好轉。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/367c408a316e4e8bba1f15c1c3b8ce3d/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250226_172540098_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        受隨後的乾燥東北季候風影響，下周初華南沿岸天氣轉涼，天色好轉。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"展望未來兩三日日間溫暖，部分時間有陽光。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c5820664cd43575be12c940d3968c0e4/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250226_172540098_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        展望未來兩三日日間溫暖，部分時間有陽光。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>本港地區下午及今晚天氣預測大致多雲，下午部分時間有陽光。吹和緩東風，初時離岸風勢清勁。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望未來兩三日日間溫暖，部分時間有陽光。本周中後期天氣潮濕，沿岸有霧。下周初天氣轉涼。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057235/即時-港聞-天氣-濕完再凍-天文台料周四五濕度高達100-冷鋒殺到下周一多區低見13°C",
