        {
            "title": "收養流浪貓變招財貓 火鍋店老闆為其開「喵界火鍋店」 供更多毛孩吃住︱有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/e05e6051fd6171efbfc286c6360c0102/15ff68e9b150478f9deeaa8ca6873746-6934b76d5684518f04455f5959652157-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ce64257f90e\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ce64257f910\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b573e4688e4830a7c2554640cc65e734/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031011560648907.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>流浪貓變招財貓！重慶一火鍋店老闆李先生去年12月收養一隻流浪貓「豆豆」，自此店裏的生意日益好轉，他為了感謝豆豆的「招財貓」體質，決定以每個月發給牠的薪水4200元（人民幣，下同），開設一家專屬於流浪貓的火鍋店，讓更多無家可歸的貓咪有食物吃、有地方住。\n\n</p><h2>以「豆豆」名義開設「七隻貓火鍋店」</h2>\n<p>據《荔枝新聞》報道，李先生表示，豆豆是在去年12月來到店裏，將牠收養後，生意突然變好許多，於是當時便開玩笑地說「豆豆給我們帶來這麼多生意，我要給牠發工資」。後來為了兌現承諾，他真的每個月給豆豆工資，並將該筆錢存下來。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-topics/3434019/%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E8%A5%BF%E5%9C%92%E5%AF%BA%E6%93%8A%E6%8E%8C%E8%B2%93%E8%88%87%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%95%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85-%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E5%8E%AD%E4%B8%96Look%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E7%87%9F%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87\">江蘇西園寺「擊掌貓」與遊客互動爆紅 周末「厭世」Look拒絕營業</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火鍋店老闆收養的流浪貓「豆豆」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/22ef557caeb0f806784133edc2f3d083/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1011_05_18_a5db5a66.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火鍋店老闆收養的流浪貓「豆豆」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火鍋店老闆與他收養的流浪貓「豆豆」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1cae5231369d011cc83b1aad0795e647/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1011_05_18_b5c428fe.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火鍋店老闆與他收養的流浪貓「豆豆」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火鍋店老闆為流浪貓開「喵界火鍋店」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fab1c2089530f3b979c921a7d26816e3/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1011_05_18_ba993297.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火鍋店老闆為流浪貓開「喵界火鍋店」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火鍋店老闆為流浪貓開「喵界火鍋店」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e7c8e97c7d427e3d15efa7bae63a92e7/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1011_05_18_eaaf0f45.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火鍋店老闆為流浪貓開「喵界火鍋店」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火鍋店老闆為流浪貓開「喵界火鍋店」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9a090441b7f8124b80131ceda34782ad/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1011_05_19_85c34d3a.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火鍋店老闆為流浪貓開「喵界火鍋店」。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「喵界火鍋店」內部。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f6b99bdf14e4c27a369c1006bec5ff2/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1011_05_19_2cb8c9ae.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「喵界火鍋店」內部。抖音@四季豆有七隻貓\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3407286/%E8%B2%93B%E7%96%91%E5%87%8D%E5%83%B5%E5%A5%84%E5%A5%84%E4%B8%80%E6%81%AF-%E5%B0%8F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E6%80%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%96%8A%E6%8C%81%E9%A2%A8%E7%AD%92%E5%90%B92%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87\">貓B疑凍僵奄奄一息 小女孩急到喊持風筒吹2小時感動網民</a>\n</p>\n<p>截至目前，豆豆累積的工資已超過1萬元，李先生突發奇想，決定以豆豆的名義開設一家名為「七隻貓火鍋店」的喵界火鍋店，專門提供流浪貓免費的食物和住所，讓牠們可隨時進來吃飯、休息。\n\n</p>\n<p>後來，已有不少流浪貓被吸引進入「七隻貓火鍋店」吃貓飼料，但由於流浪貓的警戒心較高，牠們仍然不敢進入貓窩休息。李先生提到，他會繼續提供食物和住處，等待貓咪逐漸適應環境，在未來造福更多流浪貓。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
